When formula_219 is positive, the gas temperature decreases as it passes through a throttling process, and when it is negative, the temperature increases. Therefore, the condition formula_220 defines a curve that separates the region of the formula_221 plane where formula_222 from the region where formula_223. This curve is called the &quot;inversion curve&quot;, and its equation is formula_224. Evaluating this using the expression for formula_123 derived in produces
